## 📊 SQL Queries — 25 Total

| Level | Questions | Topics |
|-------|-----------|--------|
| 🟢 Beginner (Q1–Q8) | SELECT, WHERE, GROUP BY, ORDER BY | Indian players, venues, top scorers |
| 🟡 Intermediate (Q9–Q16) | JOINs, subqueries, HAVING, CASE | All-rounders, home/away, partnerships |
| 🔴 Advanced (Q17–Q25) | CTEs, Window Functions, STDDEV | Toss analysis, form tracking, career trajectory |
